Description:
Shine bright like a diamond
Perfectly positioned in sought after Skye, this home has everything you want and more.
Boasting 4 bedrooms - master with ensuite, double vanity, walk in robe and ceiling fan, the three remaining bedrooms all have built in robes.
You will love the light and bright open plan kitchen with stainless steel appliances, pendant lighting, neutral tones, tiled splash back and tons of storage space, all flowing into the meals area and family room, rumpus room or home theatre.
Adding to this fantastic home is a formal living room, study, central family bathroom, double car garage with internal access, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, solar panels, solar hot water, huge outdoor decked entertaining area, large back yard and much more.
This immaculate family home is conveniently located close to shops, schools, public transport, sporting clubs as well as easy access to the major freeways of East Link and Peninsula Link.
There is absolutely nothing left to do apart from move in and with all these great features, this home won't wait around for long. Call now to arrange an inspection.

Description:
Living the dream
Delivering an irresistible and unbeatable kind of lifestyle that you will never need to take a vacation from; Obrien Real Estate present to you this luxury 5 bedroom home on Settlers Run, Botanic Ridge.
Positioned on a 650m2 block and backing onto third hole of the championship golf course in Settlers Run that has been designed by pro Australian golfer, Greg Norman.
Immaculately presented and built to the highest quality standard, this home boasts 3 separate living zones; including a home theatre with an excellent theatre system.
The master retreat is simply a slice of paradise! Fit for a king and queen, and equipped with a huge walk in robe, sauna as well as an ensuite with double shower and vanity. Wine and dine in your very own spa bath positioned near a beautiful window with sights to the outside landscapes.
The upper level features 4 lavishly decorated king-size bedrooms with built in desks, connecting ensuites and walk in robes. Furthermore, all bedrooms encompass their own private balconies with either views of the Melbourne CBD or the prestigious golf course of Settlers Run estate.
Sophisticated and classy, this functional home is enveloped in light and comfort with a kitchen designed for the chef at heart. Additionally, this kitchen incorporates stone benches, double ovens, a butler's pantry and gloss white cabinetry with the upmost quality appliances and fittings.
Crisp white walls, luscious carpet and porcelain tiles create a style so timeless and luxurious for the family to enjoy. The open planned living spaces awash with an abundance of natural light from the wide and bright windows.
Beyond the glass; a backyard so flawless and created to entertain family and friends during all seasons. Timber decking, an outdoor kitchen and barbecue area wrap around the wonderful pool area on looking the golf course. Stay warm and cozy outdoors with the heat lamps underneath the alfresco and gaze into the gas fire place.
Added special features also include multiple closet storage, security system with CCTV perimeter cameras and alarm, commercial grade refrigerated cooling and heating, fully established gardens and a high class laundry with built in cabinetry for all those extra items.
This house screams 'designer' and will reflect the personality and taste of those accustomed to the best in quality, design and lifestyle.

Description:
**SOLD BY PAUL RINGERI**
SUMMERHILL ESTATE, BOTANIC RIDGE: **WIDE FRONTAGE WITHIN PACES OF WETLANDS** Searching for a tranquil location? Requiring an estate offering family-friendly living? This is a sensational opportunity for those looking to upsize or downsize, while first-timers can take advantage of the Government Grants on offer and buy with confidence today!
Titled and ready to go 16 Celadon Grove is positioned in a safe and secure pocket within this prestigious up and coming estate. You will be, literally, within meters of the picturesque waterways with easy access to the Cultural Heritage Reserve and Summerhill Park. The generously sized surrounding lots cater precisely for expansive homes and provide the sense of space that local residents are seeking to enjoy. The scene is set for a lifestyle full of peace and privacy.
The allotment itself is truly a prime piece of real estate and provides the perfect foundation to create your dream home! Regular in shape the land measures a healthy 512m2 with a wide frontage of 16m and a depth of 32m. The existing fencing is sure to be an immediate money saver and there is ample room for an array of different styles and designs!
Summerhill is setting a new standard in Botanic Ridge with special and considered features that make the community unique. An exclusive address for fewer than 200 spacious and elegant homes, this community has been designed to blend in perfectly with the natural environment surrounding. Nestled in between the Royal Botanic Gardens and the popular Acacia community, the estate includes a formal estate entrance point, beautifully landscaped parks, native streetscapes, charming natural stone accents, designed wetlands and wide tree-lined streets.
Other features include Botanic Village, a local shopping hub positioned in the neighboring estate, Acacia, complete with its own supermarket, cafe and specialty stores, primary school and a community centre. Sports and recreational fields have also been proposed!
Sensational location within close proximity to all of the amenities on offer in the established townships of Cranbourne and Pearcedale. If you are a golf enthusiast chuck the clubs in the boot as the well known 18-hole Greg Norman designed course is literally minutes away.
Call today before it's GOING, GOING ..... GONE!
CONTACT US TO ARRANGE FOR A TIME TO VIEW THE SECTION 32 VENDOR STATEMENT!

Description:
BRAND NEW, WITH ALL THE LUXURIES!
5 SAVAGE WAY, CLYDE NORTH
This home is built with you in mind. Offering the very best in family living; the home is designed to be functional and adaptable for todays ever changing busy lifestyles. Built to an exceptional quality, for you to move straight into or invest if you wish to!
Featuring four spacious bedrooms plus study. Generous 2 living areas. Two bathrooms plus 2 powder rooms. Master with full ensuite with twin vanities and walk in robe downstairs. The hallway from the entrance leads to a large open plan meal and family living area, adjacent to central hostess kitchen. Kitchen comes with 900mm appliances and Stone benchtops, walk in pantry. Completing this family home are the advantages of a double lock up garage.
With access to public transport, including the nearby Cranbourne train station, and surrounded by a variety of education facilities with primary and secondary schools.
At the heart of the Delaray community (now award winning estate for residential development award of over 250 lots), the architecturally designed Club Delaray is a place to connect, to meet up and relax with friends, family and neighbours who, like you, have chosen the unique Delaray lifestyle.
Within easy walking distance of your new home, at Club Delaray the choice is yours. Work out in the gymnasium, laze by the pool, enjoy a coffee with friends or relax in the library with your favourite magazine.
The community garden and Mens Shed, both part of the Club complex, are great for pursuing new hobbies, reconnecting with old ones and for meeting people. This precinct is the hub around which a healthy, connected community will revolve.
The inclusions to this home given below.
Caesar Stone bench top in kitchen bathroom and ensuite
Stainless steel appliances
European design fittings and fixtures
Front and back landscaping and drive way
Heating and cooling
Fly screen
Window furnishings: roller blinds
Fencing
6 Star energy rating
Feature facades
High ceiling
Square set cornices
ONLY one thing left to do...

Description:
Double storey, renovated family home
Located in Central Cranbourne, this much loved family home is now up for grabs. Conveniently positioned just minutes' walk to Cranbourne West primary school and Cranbourne West Coles and local shops and medical centre. Enjoying easy access to the major arterials and less than 5 minutes' drive to the Cranbourne Train Station & Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, there is much more this property could offer in the way of an excellent location.
Set on a generous & flat 640 sqm(approx.) block, this beautiful renovated family home features 4 bedrooms with built in robes, 2 baths, open plan kitchen with gas cooking, very spacious living area, wooden floors, air conditioners, beautiful veranda, nicely maintained garden with a storage shed, massive secured 4 car garage, 12 solar panels and much more.
Be quick to inspect as this property will not last long. So call Vikram on 0430392918 or Ajay on 0403351577 for further details.

Description:
Bespoke Family Home With 2 Living Zones
OFFERS CLOSING 26TH JUNE @ 5PM.
This well maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has unique features and premium inclusions that you won't find in most places. It was constructed by Boutique homes to extremely high standards and has been maintained impeccably. If you're looking for a like new, bespoke family home with premium inclusions, then this property is perfect for you.
The main open-plan living space is light and airy with beautiful timber floors, and seamless access to a decked alfresco space. The contemporary kitchen is stylish and functional featuring a white stone top island with breakfast bar, quality appliances, including dishwasher, and ample cabinet space. Choose to relax here after a long day or enjoy some family time in the additional living space which can double as a home theatre.
The master bedroom is inviting with a large WIR and en-suite, complete with floating wooden grain vanity. The additional bedrooms are a good size with large windows, carpeted floors and BIRs, while the family bathroom features a bath, shower and separate WC, plus a laundry.
Main features include:
- Boutique Homes builder with unique features & premium inclusions
- Spacious open-plan kitchen/living/dining
- Gorgeous decked alfresco with feature wall
- Dual living zones
- Master bedroom with en-suite & WIR
- Timber floorboards & quality carpet
- Feature lighting throughout
- Solar panels for energy efficiency
- Central heating, split units & ceiling fans
- Landscaped garden with shed in backyard
- Single garage with internal access
This property is located in a family-friendly neighbourhood with amenities like Casey Fields Sport Complex, parks and playgrounds, schools and shopping centres within close vicinity, making it a smart choice for families, investors, downsizers and first home buyers alike.
If premium living is what you're looking for, then this bespoke family home is for you. To view this outstanding property, book an inspection with our team today!

Description:
When Location Counts & Quality Matters...
A home unlike any other, standing strong over the past five years with a massive 16m frontage on approx. 512Sqm of land. Gorgeous landscaped gardens greet you, coupled with the oversized garage with rear roller door access, youre in for a treat.
This home casts warmth and absolute class from the moment you step through the front door, wide hallways and high ceilings that lead to the luxurious master bedroom with expansive WIR and ensuite with dual vanity and double shower with extra-large niche. The remaining three bedrooms all large in size with access to separate the study nook and main family bathroom.
Spacious kitchen including stone bench tops, built in 5 burner cooktop, oversize oven, extended central island benchtop and dishwasher, all overlooking the sunlit dining area and the main living room with wall mounted gas fireplace casting a nice glow as you relax on the couch on a cold winters day. Also with nearby access to the spacious rumpus with extra-large windows for views of exquisite gardens.
The backyard has everything youre looking for, alfresco with skylights, decking which is complemented with exposed aggregate, pavers to the garden shed surrounded by beautiful landscaped gardens. An entertainers backyard that will surely exceed all expectations.

Description:
THE PERFECT ONE STOP SHOP - SPACIOUS ENTERTAINING, OVERSIZED GARAGE PLUS REAR ROLLER ACCESS!
CASIANA GROVE ESTATE, CRANBOURNE WEST: **TRIPLE SIZE GARAGE WITH PLENTY OF SPACE FOR A HOME GYM, BONUS STORAGE FACILITIES, A WORKSHOP/MAN CAVE & GENERAL PARKING** In recent years this ever popular pocket has flourished into a neighbourhood favoured by young families thanks to its abundance of parkland and open space combined with the availability of local amenities and various education options. 69 Everlasting Boulevard is a real standout and presents as a complete package with display like presentation plus an impressive low maintenance set up!
Fronted by an appealing facade, this immaculate Burbank built family home makes you feel instantly at ease as soon as you step through the front door. With copious amount of natural light there is an endless list of features that include a generous tiled lounge/dining room that accompanies the gorgeous hostess kitchen. Complete with stone benchtops, glass splashback and stainless steel appliances this has to be one of the main selling attractions!
There are 4 robed bedrooms to comfort any growing family, the master with a walk in wardrobe and a lovely ensuite to match the separate family bathroom. Ducted heating and 2 split-system air conditioners provide seasonal respite and don't forget the powerful 6.0kW solar array to help keep the power bills in check.
Step outside and be greeted by an oversized remote double garage with bonus workshop facilities and rear roll through access en route the the picturesque rear yard. The focal point of this area is the extensive decked pergola that makes for the perfect space to entertain 24/7 ... rain, hail or shine!
Casiana Grove, a place where rest and play is always nearby, is in close proximity to the proposed Cranbourne West Secondary College and a wealth of recreational options and amenities including the local Clarinda Park shopping centre. Golf enthusiasts will be thrilled to find that their new home is neighbouring the Ranfurlie Golf Club. Nature lovers will also take delight in exploring over 300 hectares of native bush land at the nearby Royal Botanic Gardens. For a faster pace, head to the Cranbourne Racecourse and try your luck with a trifecta!
Close to Cranbourne's city centre, everything you need is within range including quality medical facilities. You'll be spoilt for choice for your children's education with a multitude of additional schools on offer, including Barton Primary School and the esteemed Casey Grammar and St. Peter's Catholic College. If a retail fix is in need, head to the recently reformed Cranbourne Park shopping centre, or grab a bite to eat at the multitude of restaurants and funky cafes positioned right throughout the City of Casey.
Those working inner city will appreciate the close proximity to both the Cranbourne and Merinda Park train stations with convenient access to Eastlink also nearby. Not to mention the local bus stops as well!
This terrific package is bound to walk out the door so call before it's SELLING, SELLING, SOLD!
**SELLING IN CONJUNCTION WITH PROPERTY ASSIST VICTORIA - Cameron Miller-Randle**
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW - PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS!

Description:
PRIME LOCATION AND WETLAND VIEWS
BROMPTON ESTATE: Normally that is all we have to say. But with this ideal location there is just so much more to tell you about. This is the estate for true family friendly living. Close to everything and all services in place. 12 Amarillo Drive Cranbourne South!
On offer is a piece of prime real estate and ready for you to create your dream home for your family. The lifestyle on the Brompton Estate has been built on quality throughout. Stage 1 of Brompton offers this 611 m2 regular shape block with a frontage of 19.5 m and depth of 34.4 m. The outlook is special. A wetland aspect that is beginning to be one of the most talked about features of the estate. Choose your builder and your plans and the exciting journey begins.
Brompton is set amongst 17 hectares of open space. There is 11 hectares of wetlands and waterways, 5 local pocket parks together with over 10 kilometres of interconnected walking and cycling trails throughout the development. Theres even an onsite retail centre complete with shopping facilities, local services and a supermarket.
For those working in the inner city, its only approx. 45 minutes away and you will appreciate the close proximity to both Cranbourne and Merinda Park train stations together with the convenience of having the Eastlink nearby. There is easy access to both private and public schooling and you are completely surrounded by an abundance of entertainment and recreational options including the Cranbourne Race Track, Casey RACE, offering both Gym and pool facilities as well as the ever-expanding Casey Fields.
This location is second to none with easy access to Western Port Highway, which leads to all the established amenities on offer in the popular suburbs of Cranbourne, Carrum Downs, Lyndhurst, Hampton Park and Dandenong. Cranbourne is the gateway to the Mornington Peninsula with an abundance of wineries, whilst a relaxing weekend down at Philip Island will always be on the cards.
Section 32 Vendor Statement is available.

Description:
Relaxed Lifestyle on 1-acre/ 4,850sqm approx.
The opportunity is here to own a peaceful slice of Cranbourne South property situated on approx. 1-acre/ 4,850sqm. Step away from the hustle and bustle of city living and live among the native birdlife, yet keep your busy lifestyle running with central Cranbourne only moments away!
Set back from the street and surrounded by lush, green surrounds, this originally presented 3-bedroom charmer is the relaxed forever home that you've been searching for. Sit back and unwind in front of the wood-fired Coonara in the expansive living and dining zones, extending through to the spacious retro kitchen with electric cooking. Upstairs, three large bedrooms (two with built-in robes) anchor one of two bathrooms and a retreat/second lounge. Plan your modern makeover and turn this house into a home (STCA), or keep as is for the ideal investment or comfortable choice, complete with split system heating and cooling, large picture windows, oversized laundry and second bathroom/shower room.
Parking won't ever be an issue, with its single carport and extensive driveway with plenty of room to store all vehicles from cars to boats and caravans with a single carport. It's time to experience the way life is supposed to be; relaxing, peaceful and all encapsulated in this immaculate bush block.

Description:
CLASSY & FRESH 4 BEDDER
Here it is, the class factor you all need in a great family home. Need to entertain, or show off? This recently renovated home is the one to inspect! All the hard work has been done and all you need to do is move in! If you're in the market for a first home or investment here is a great opportunity.
Features include:
- Master at the front of the home with own ensuite and walk in robes.
- 2 Very large semi-separate living areas.
- Bed 2 & 3 with BIR and 4th bedroom/study.
- Fully renovated kitchen that makes the home feel amazing with stainless steel freestanding oven/gas cooktop, dishwasher and ample cupboard space.
- Separate bathroom with vanity, shower and bathtub.
- Ducted heating and evaporative cooling with NBN available.
- 22 SOLAR PANELS!!! Barely any electricity bills!
- Large outdoor area overlooking a grassed yard perfect for the kids or pets.
- Large double garage with rear roller door access to fit caravans/trailers/boats etc.
Don't miss out on this great home, just 5min drive to Duff Street shopping Centre & Cranbourne West Primary School, or a 25-minute WALK to the Cranbourne Train Station, lots of hidden parks, walking tracks and dont forget all the amenities at your finger tips with the new Woolworths (Cranbourne west) just a 3min drive away.
With so much happing in Cranbourne West this property will not last long so contact Simon Murphy today!

Description:
Exceptional Living & Invaluable Address
Surrounded by well-presented homes in renown Casiana Estate, this impeccable single-level residence achieves the perfect balance of light, space and family function in a premier location of Cranbourne West. Meticulously designed and built, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is comprehensively appointed with stunning finishes with an emphasis on open living and alfresco entertaining for a sophisticated low-maintenance lifestyle.
Primed for all stages of family life, three living zones include a lovely sitting room or formal lounge and a theatre room towards the rear is inviting and comfortable. A domain for any season, the fabulous outdoor entertaining alfresco area is accessible through the sliding doors. Further defining features in this area include timber decking overlooking the low maintenance backyard.
A modern kitchen offers stone benchtop loaded with ample storage and breakfast bar, a suite of stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, 900mm gas cooktop, wall oven, glass splashback, rangehood and built-in cabinetry
The main bedroom suite enjoys large ensuite featuring include stone benchtop, oversized mirror, floor-to- ceiling tiles in shower base, 2-pac cabinets, oversized shower, double vanity and walk-in robe. Three further bedrooms with built-in robes are served by a beautiful family bathroom and separate toilet.
The location is second to none with easy access to Western Port Highway, which leads to all of the established amenities on offer in the popular suburbs of Cranbourne, Carrum Downs, Lyndhurst, Hampton Park and Dandenong! Cranbourne is the gateway to the Mornington Peninsula with an abundance of wineries, whilst a relaxing weekend down at Philip Island will always be on the card.
Close proximity to Ranfurlie Golf Club, Barton Primary School, the Mayone Bulluk Family and Community Centre, parklands, friendly dog park and the Clarinda Village Shopping Centre just meters away. Everything is right with this home from price to location to convenience.
Goldbank TEAM Welcomes you and looks forward to meeting you at the opens.
